---
// On The Work — DDD research narrative.
---
<section class="section on-the-work" id="on-the-work" data-section-id="on-the-work">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <h2 data-color-letters data-inertial-text>on the work</h2>
    <article class="ddd-card">
      <header class="ddd-header">
        <h3>Disconnected Data Distribution (DDD)</h3>
        <p class="role">
          Undergraduate Research Assistant · Reed Systems Group, SJSU · From Sept. 2025
        </p>
      </header>
      <div class="story">
        <p>
          Over the last year, I've gotten the opportunity to work on DDD. Working with
          labmates and Dr. Ben Reed, we utilize WiFi-Direct to create a system of internet
          where internet is gone — whether due to natural disaster, war, and the like — for
          free, utilizing current infrastructure.
        </p>
        <p>
          Think of a villager who wants to send a message: when they send it using
          WiFi-Direct, that message, encrypted, makes it to say a bus driver's phone who is
          driving to where there is internet, where the villager's message is amplified.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="project-links ddd-links" role="list" aria-label="DDD links">
        <a
          class="project-link"
          role="listitem"
          href="https://sjsu-cs-systems-group.github.io/discdd.net/index.html"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          <span class="project-link-icon" aria-hidden="true">⊕</span>
          <span class="project-link-label">about</span>
        </a>
        <a
          class="project-link"
          role="listitem"
          href="https://github.com/SJSU-CS-systems-group/DDD"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          <span class="project-link-icon" aria-hidden="true">↗</span>
          <span class="project-link-label">github</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .ddd-card {
    background: var(--ink-1);
    border-left: 2px solid var(--accent-on-the-work);
    padding: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);
    border-radius: 0 4px 4px 0;
    max-width: 56rem;
  }
  .ddd-header {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .ddd-header h3 {
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }
  .role {
    font-size: var(--type-small);
    color: var(--paper-2);
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }
  .story p {
    color: var(--paper-1);
    max-width: 48rem;
  }
  .story p + p {
    margin-top: 1em;
  }

  .ddd-links {
    margin-top: 1.25rem;
  }
</style>
